                        "plain": "Hey, it's Zeno Rocha.\r\n\r\n2025 is here, and we finished the year by shipping several improvements. But\r\nbefore we get to that, I want to ask you one thing:\r\n\r\nWhat should Resend build, fix, or improve in 2025?\r\nHit \"Reply\" and let me know — I read every reply.\r\n\r\nOkay, here are some of the latest news...\r\n\r\n\r\nTOP DELIVERABILITY TIPS FOR 2025\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://youtu.be/eDoHvKiB2Lc\r\n\r\nWe regularly share tips for landing in the inbox and packaged our top 10 tips\r\ninto a 4-minute video. Are you following these pro tips?\r\n\r\n→ Watch the video https://youtu.be/eDoHvKiB2Lc\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nBUILDING YOUR OWN X/TWITTER COMPONENT\r\n\r\nhttps://resend.com/blog/design-engineering-an-x-component\r\n\r\nWe recently released a new component for embedding tweets\r\nhttps://resend.com/changelog/new-x-twitter-component in your Broadcasts. Our new\r\nDesigner Engineer, Danilo Woznica, wrote a deep dive on the technical process of\r\ncreating the component.\r\n\r\n→ Read the technical post\r\nhttps://resend.com/blog/design-engineering-an-x-component\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nCRUCIAL EMAILS FOR HEALTHCARE\r\n\r\nhttps://resend.com/customers/hike-medical\r\n\r\nHike Medical delivers employee healthcare benefits. Their ability to reliably\r\ncommunicate directly impacts how many people benefit from their solutions, and\r\ndrives their revenue and growth.\r\n\r\nLearn how they are using Resend to send both transactional and marketing emails.\r\n\r\n→ Read the Hike Medical story https://resend.com/customers/hike-medical\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n2024 YEAR IN REVIEW\r\n\r\nhttps://resend.com/blog/new-features-in-2024\r\n\r\nLet's recap some of the best features Resend launched in 2024.\r\n\r\n→ Read the post https://resend.com/blog/new-features-in-2024\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nNEW INTEGRATIONS\r\n\r\nHere are some of the most recent integrations:\r\n\r\n * New Tinybird Integration\r\n   https://www.tinybird.co/docs/get-data-in/guides/ingest-from-resend\r\n\r\n * New SuprSend Integration https://docs.suprsend.com/docs/resend\r\n\r\n * New Coolify Integration\r\n   https://coolify.io/docs/knowledge-base/notifications/#resend-configuration\r\n\r\nWe’re excited to see even more tools integrate with Resend in 2025.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nHappy sending,\r\nZeno Rocha\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\nYou are receiving this email as a user of Resend.\r\n\r\nWant to change how you receive these emails?\r\nYou can unsubscribe from this list https://unsubscribe.resend.com/?token=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..YurAOMeWDXIRWIO7Q_9hKF5WLrZv0bw5k2kDcyv65iI.\r\n\r\n2261 Market Street #5039\r\nSan Francisco, CA 94114\r\n\r\n",
